title: Pretty much a bust
author: VD
content_html:
Well, there was a fourth “celebrity” death this weekend, but I tend to doubt the possible suicide of an unknown actor from a show no one ever watched was the sort of thing that Q meant when he warned of a “suicide weekend” being a signal of arrests to come.

The Goldbergs actor Jackson Odell is found dead in a sober living home in California, aged 20

I have to admit, I was a little disappointed to learn that The Goldbergs was not a show about the whacky shenanigans of a National Review editor-at-large and the wise-cracking mother with whom he lives.
